summary: In case you wonder where I am at, I’m just had the misfortune of meeting the ship Yoonmin which is part of a kpop group named...
body:
In case you wonder where I am at, I’m just had the misfortune of meeting the ship Yoonmin which is part of a kpop group named bts. I know I know what you must be thinking but don’t worry I’m not completely all over them, but the thing is, I needed to know all that I missed and there is a lot. the worse part is, this type of fandom, the content never ends, and the analyses over it never does either. Also a lot of time goes now to learning some of their choegraphies cause I love them. And I’m not even into the whole thing or the other ships! (I mean their music is awesome af) But this shows what kind of bottomless pit I fell into. 

I still love aokise with all my heart. I just feel guilty about not finding time to squeeze my writing in my daily schedule. I hope I will. It would be a shame otherwise with all the plotlines I had in store.
